212
00:13:51,760 --> 00:13:54,090
Velmistr. <br> <i> (film 2013) </i>

213
00:13:54,090 --> 00:13:56,220
Jsi docela literární.

214
00:13:56,800 --> 00:13:58,530
Za několik hodin,

215
00:13:58,530 --> 00:14:01,070
